text: Inermoleiopus fuscosignatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1977.Biolib.cz - Inermoleiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1977 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
